msgid ""
"Klein for Ray source layout, package ownership rules, public API "
"boundaries, and architecture checks."
msgstr "Klein for Ray 的源码布局、包所有权规则、公共 API 边界和架构检查。"

msgid "Package structure"
msgstr "包结构"

msgid ""
"Klein for Ray uses a conventional `src` layout. The importable package is"
" under `src/ray/klein`; tests, examples, and documentation do not live "
"inside the runtime package."
msgstr "Klein for Ray 使用常规的 `src` 布局。可导入的包位于 `src/ray/klein`；测试、示例和文档不放在运行时包内。"

msgid "Import public APIs"
msgstr "导入公共 API"

msgid "Applications should start with the short, stable imports:"
msgstr "应用应从简短、稳定的导入开始："

msgid ""
"`StreamSink` remains public for advanced selective execution, but "
"ordinary applications register terminals and call `ray.klein.execute"
"(\"job-name\")` without importing it."
msgstr ""
"`StreamSink` 仍是面向高级选择性执行的公开类型，但普通应用只需注册终结操作并调用 "
"`ray.klein.execute(\"job-name\")`，无需导入它。"

msgid ""
"The package `__init__` modules lazily resolve public names. Internal "
"modules continue to import from the module that defines a symbol; they do"
" not import through a convenience re-export. This keeps dependency cycles"
" visible."
msgstr "包的 `__init__` 模块会延迟解析公共名称。内部模块仍从定义符号的模块导入，而不通过便捷的重导出导入。这样可让依赖循环保持可见。"

msgid "Follow naming and ownership rules"
msgstr "遵循命名和所有权规则"

msgid ""
"A public class is defined in a snake-case module with the corresponding "
"name: `DataStream` lives in `data_stream.py`, `StateHandle` in "
"`state_handle.py`, and so on."
msgstr ""
"公共类应定义在对应名称的蛇形命名模块中：`DataStream` 位于 `data_stream.py`，`StateHandle` 位于 "
"`state_handle.py`，依此类推。"

msgid ""
"A public module normally defines one public class. Small private helper "
"classes may remain beside the implementation that exclusively owns them."
msgstr "一个公共模块通常定义一个公共类。仅由某项实现拥有的小型私有辅助类可以留在该实现旁边。"

msgid ""
"Package `__init__.py` files contain exports and package documentation, "
"not implementations."
msgstr "包的 `__init__.py` 文件只包含导出和包文档，不包含实现。"

msgid ""
"`api` owns user contracts and graph construction. `runtime` implements "
"those contracts. An integration depends on contracts, configuration, and "
"source-owned state rather than scheduler internals."
msgstr "`api` 负责用户约定和图构建，`runtime` 实现这些约定。集成依赖约定、配置和数据源自有状态，而不依赖调度器内部实现。"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"`_internal` is not a compatibility promise. New application code must not"
" import it. Some top-level bridge names currently resolve into "
"`_internal` for the bundled CLI/runtime; they remain non-application APIs"
" as described in the {doc}`top-level namespace reference "
"<api/top_level>`."
msgstr ""
"`_internal` 不提供兼容性承诺。新的应用代码不得导入它。当前部分顶层桥接名称会解析到 `_internal`，供内置 "
"CLI/运行时使用；如 {doc}`顶层命名空间参考 <api/top_level>` 所述，它们仍不是应用 API。"

msgid ""
"Generic buckets such as `common`, `core`, `utils`, and `entity` are not "
"architectural layers. A helper moves to the domain that owns it, or into "
"`_internal` when it is genuinely cross-cutting and private."
msgstr ""
"`common`、`core`、`utils` 和 `entity` "
"等通用桶并不是架构层。辅助代码应移至拥有它的领域；若它确实跨领域且为私有代码，则移至 `_internal`。"

msgid "Check dependency boundaries"
msgstr "检查依赖边界"

msgid ""
"Architecture tests enforce package boundaries and the one-public-class "
"convention in stable packages. Ruff validates imports, exception "
"handling, and cyclomatic complexity. Full verification also imports the "
"top-level API, builds the wheel and source distribution, and runs "
"documentation checks."
msgstr ""
"架构测试会在稳定包中强制执行包边界和单公共类约定。Ruff 验证导入、异常处理和圈复杂度。完整验证还会导入顶层 API、构建 wheel "
"和源码发行包，并运行文档检查。"

msgid ""
"See [Architecture](architecture.md) for how these packages collaborate "
"during planning, streaming execution, checkpointing, and recovery."
msgstr "关于这些包在规划、流处理执行、检查点和恢复期间如何协作，请参阅[架构](architecture.md)。"
